item.title: Hw o i get loged in
item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

Ok when it shows up the login screen on moparscape client. Click “login” and then type any username and password you want. Then type in the ip address of the server (I.E. freescape.servegame.com) and click “login”. If it doesnt work then:

  1. Username already taken on that server (just that one, not all servers)

  2. Server is not online

  3. You are banned from server (rare from happening)

I hope I helped you so Enjoy!

~Mod Taharok
